{"tid":603360,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚睇南極 喊到收唔到聲","createTime":"2018-03-23T16:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T01:54:53.000Z","uid":87132,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"260e78ad6cff3e90f866cdc81a922ce92c054fb7","tid":603360,"uid":87132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"其實對上一次 好有感觸<br />\n就係Clannad <br />\n<br />\n本身見住佢數銀紙 一路數一路講自己係打邊份工得到 已經個心嗱住嗱住<br />\n到咗打開電腦 無數寄比媽媽嘅mail<br />\n真係一發不可收拾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有失去過親人 唔多唔少都會明果種感覺<br />\n以前嘅錄音、留言 一言一語<br />\n一路睇都會眼濕濕<br />\n今次我Mr.Kid 都全力g chi 南極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係友情 親情都比佢玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e1653b5eda3ffe7d9d998f13bb1e17b2e47765","tid":603360,"uid":50131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:30:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宇宙霸權</span></span>"},{"pid":"c78fe66d3600744305214dd75dc7a16d5032d01a","tid":603360,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"乜黎"},{"pid":"2e506c888e9e51a06c801f398f55ded7807b9621","tid":603360,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c78fe66d3600744305214dd75dc7a16d5032d01a","tid":603360,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"乜黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"鼠快睇!"},{"pid":"39556ed2b4f196d6391acfb879df78a965b5e7e6","tid":603360,"uid":13138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:51:12.000Z","msg":"比宇宙更遠的地方"},{"pid":"d84445097a4f9c5155cc65bb821f7a9b3b0e0281","tid":603360,"uid":149878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39556ed2b4f196d6391acfb879df78a965b5e7e6","tid":603360,"uid":13138,"like":1,"dislike":1